href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.307105046&amp;id=fig06c">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig07" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.307105046/asset/images/105046fig07.jpeg" height="1095" width="1280" aria-labelledby="fig07" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 7</span> Diagram shows an accessory diaphragm (arrowhead) as a band running obliquely in the lower right hemithorax and joining the diaphragm. Right inferior pulmonary vessels pass through a hole in the accessory diaphragm (arrow) and supply the separated lung parenchyma below the accessory diaphragm.<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.307105046&amp;id=fig07">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.307105046/asset/images/105046fig08a.jpeg" height="1350" width="1350" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 8a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.307105046&amp;id=fig08a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.307105046/asset/images/105046fig08b.jpeg" height="1800" width="1750" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 8b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.307105046&amp;id=fig08b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08c" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.307105046/asset/images/105046fig08c.jpeg" height="1692" 