uzawa M. Radiographic changes in the diaphragm after repair of congenital diaphragmatic hernia. <em>J Pediatr Surg</em> 2008;43(12):2156–2160.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jpedsurg.2008.08.042">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19040925/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Radiographic+changes+in+the+diaphragm+after+repair+of+congenital+diaphragmatic+hernia&amp;author=S+Kamata&amp;author=N+Usui&amp;author=T+Sawai&amp;author=K+Nose&amp;author=M+Kamiyama&amp;author=M+Fukuzawa&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;journal=J+Pediatr+Surg&amp;pages=2156-2160&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.jpedsurg.2008.08.042&amp;pmid=19040925">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">36.</div><div id="r36" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Mallick MS, Alqahtani A. Laparoscopic-assisted repair of Morgagni hernia in children. <em>J Pediatr Surg</em> 2009;44(8):1621–1624.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jpedsurg.2008.10.108">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19635315/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Laparoscopic-assisted+repair+of+Morgagni+hernia+in+children&amp;author=MS+Mallick&amp;author=A+Alqahtani&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=J+Pediatr+Surg&amp;pages=1621-1624&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.jpedsurg.2008.10.108&amp;pmid=19635315">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">37.</div><div id="r37" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Karpelowsky JS, Wieselthaler N, Rode H. Primary paraesophageal hernia in children