32">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15486911/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Primary+germ+cell+tumor+of+the+diaphragm&amp;author=J+Traubici&amp;author=A+Daneman&amp;author=A+Hayes-Jordan&amp;author=A+Fecteau&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=J+Pediatr+Surg&amp;pages=1578-1580&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.jpedsurg.2004.06.032&amp;pmid=15486911">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
